<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="EDFLetterText" style="margin-left: 0.5in;"><font style="" size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">Dear {!Climate_Corps_Engagement__c.Fellow_first_name__c},</font></p><p class="EDFLetterText" style="margin-left: 0.5in;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="EDFLetterText" style="margin-left: 0.5in;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">Congratulations! I am pleased to inform you that your host organization has confirmed your fellowship placement. Our team is excited to welcome you to the Climate Corps Class of 2023, and we look forward to working with you this summer!&nbsp;</font></p><p class="EDFLetterText" style="margin-left: 0.5in;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="EDFLetterText" style="margin-left: 0.5in;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">Here are the most immediate next steps for you:&nbsp;</font></p><p class="EDFLetterText" style="margin-left: 0.5in;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="EDFLetterText" style="margin-left: 0.5in;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">1. Log into the <a href="https://environmentaldefensefund.my.site.com/EDFCCFellowPortal/s/login">Fellow Portal</a>. You should find that it's updated, with a new tile called "Portal Deliverables." Within, you'll find the first thing to do is watch the Fellow Orientation Webinar. Please watch it within the next two days.&nbsp;</font></p><p class="EDFLetterText" style="margin-left: 0.5in;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="EDFLetterText" style="margin-left: 0.5in;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">2. Review the other items required throughout the Spring in preparation for your Fellowship.&nbsp;</font></p><p class="EDFLetterText" style="margin-left: 0.5in;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif"><br></font></p><p class="EDFLetterText" style="margin-left: 0.5in;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">3. Complete a 15-minute Orientation Call with me, your Engagement Manager (or EM), after you have watched the webinar. Come with questions!&nbsp;</font></p><p class="EDFLetterText" style="margin-left: 0.5in;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="EDFLetterText" style="margin-left: 0.5in;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">As a reminder, as a Climate Corps fellow, you agree to fulfill the duties as outlined in the 2023 Climate Corps Fellow Agreement. Reneging on your commitment to be a Climate Corps fellow may result in a breach in your University's recruiting policies and honor code.&nbsp;</font></p><p class="EDFLetterText" style="margin-left: 0.5in;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">&nbsp;</font></p><p class="EDFLetterText" style="margin-left: 0.5in;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">Thank you and congratulations!&nbsp;</font></p><p class="EDFLetterText" style="margin-left: 0.5in;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">Best,&nbsp;</font></p><p class="EDFLetterText" style="margin-left: 0.5in;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">{!Climate_Corps_Engagement__c.EDF_Engagement_Manager__c}</font></p><p class="EDFLetterText" style="margin-left: 0.5in;"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">Climate Corps</font></p><p class="EDFLetterText" style="margin-left: 0.5in;"><font style="" size="2" face="Verdana, Helvetica, sans-serif">EDFClimateCorps.org</font></p><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div>]]></td>
